{"tid":505428,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"不誠實使用電腦罪","createTime":"2017-12-21T06:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T06:10:58.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c1770af9ce29b9c72d838819de66fd2c5458a9","tid":505428,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"《證據條例》、《稅務條例》及《商業登記條例》界定「電腦」一詞，定義實質上是「儲存、處理或重新取得資料的任何裝置」<br />\n<br />\n所以，律政司話，智能手機都係電腦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130413/mobile/odn-20130413-0413_00176_105.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130413%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20130413-0413_00176_105.html&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2FwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=e6032521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130413/mobile/odn-20130413-0413_00176_105.html</a><br />\n<br />\n不誠實意圖使用電腦，即係犯法<br />\n<br />\n咁連登仔，咁多藍絲，紅巴，其實係咪已經犯左法？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，如果有人申請網上account，亂填地址，或電話，或收入，或性別，係咪又已經犯左法？"},{"pid":"061fdb84fdc18bc5a6f8ce4c5d3bb270752782bb","tid":505428,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"咁不誠實嘅定義係乜"},{"pid":"718356693192d3319797a6fae56ec50241561646","tid":505428,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁不誠實嘅定義係乜</blockquote><br />\n反政府囉"}]}